update   :- update statement is used to modify the existing records in a table. 

drop     :- drop statement is used to delete the entire table .

truncate :- truncate statement is used to delete the data In the table with in a single shot . 

delete   :- delete statement is used TO delete the records from a table using step by step method . 

Syntax :- 

update :-
   update employee
   set  eid=12 where ename='Ramya'

  drop :- 
  drop table employee 

  truncate :- 
    truncate table employee 

  delete 
    delete from employee where eid=8
